title: László Czéh
text:
László Czéh (born 1 February 1968) is a Hungarian retired <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Career.
In the <a href="1998%E2%80%9399%20Liga%20Artzit">1998/99</a> season, Czeh scored 19 goals for <a href="Maccabi%20Netanya">Maccabi Netanya</a> to clinch the title of Israel best goalscorer in the second league.
